10c ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">这个现象被当地许多人亲眼所见。 </div><div class="t m0 x23 h4 y21e ffd fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">还有<span class="_ _21"> </span>1958 年，<span class="_ _28"></span>当时正逢解放期间，<span class="_ _28"></span>藏地有着翻天覆地的</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
